reviewText:
This video is great for those who remember the Max Fleisher Popeye and the a.a.p. movie Popeye as well. The video and audio are refreshingly clear and the cartoons are true Popeye stuff, not the later watered down t.v. stuff  by the same name.
I would have gone for the 5 stars if it were all Max  Fleisher....but I guess some people have to have the color stuff.
